N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 111.9 - Control of insects and diseases

State Regulations

Stands or trees from which seed is to be taken for
certification shall show evidence that reasonable precaution has been taken to
control insects and diseases harmful to seeds or seed
production. Notes
